# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values (not committed to git for security).

```
BOT_TOKEN=your_discord_bot_token_here
NODE_ENV=production
```

## How to get your bot token

1. Go to https://discord.com/developers/applications
2. Click "New Application" and give it a name
3. Go to the "Bot" tab and click "Add Bot"
4. Under the TOKEN section, click "Copy" to copy your token
5. Paste it as `BOT_TOKEN` in your `.env` file

⚠️ **NEVER commit your `.env` file or share your bot token!**
